subject: But if the same thing happened today, I should keep it.
body:
I would suggest you start with an owner drawn 
listbox which displays the icons. Now exit the room and work your way back down stairs.
They would only have to go twenty-four hours 
without, food. The "label" you make reference to can be a column.
Lock Physical Record Set. GetO 0000CC20 45 4D 43 50 
00 00 47 65 74 41 43 50 00 00 47 65 EMCP.
It is the reason I have contacted you.
Make an 'OEM installation diskette' or equivalent 
installation source directory for IsoUsb.
InqSoft Translation Tool 2.
